* Overall awards wrapper
*
* Purpose:          Runs OVERALL.RSM to list top finishers, then EXCLUDE.RSM
*                   to exclude them from subsequent age-group results.
*
* Param 1 (%1):     Number of overall winners (e.g., 3).
* Param 2 (%2):     Sex label (FEMALE or MALE).
* Param 3 (%3):     Sex code (F or M).
*
* Example:          @OVERALL.RSM 3 FEMALE F
*
OVERALL.RSM %1 %2 %3
EXCLUDE.RSM %1 %2 %3
